abstract: Investors cautiously pulled back as political moves failed to end a federal budget standoff. | The head of the Commodity Futures Trading Commission’s enforcement unit is poised to step down. | A study raises doubts about the value of consultants to pensions. | With the second anniversary of Occupy comes a prepaid debit card.
